<item>
            <title>[LU-7434] lost bulk leads to a hang</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7434</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The reverse order of request_out_callback() and reply_in_callback() puts the RPC into UNREGISTERING state, which is waiting for RPC &amp;amp; bulk md unlink, whereas only RPC md unlink has been called so far. If bulk is lost, even expired_set does not check for UNREGISTERING state.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The same for write if server returns an error.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
